long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing "Jokelaty" - Your Daily Dose of Laughter in Your Chrome Browser!

Jokelaty is the ultimate Google Chrome extension designed to brighten up your day with a touch of dad jokes. With a simple click, this delightful extension brings a wave of laughter straight to your browser, making your online experience more enjoyable and entertaining.

Get ready to chuckle, giggle, and laugh out loud as Jokelaty delivers a fresh and hilarious joke every time you open a new tab or with just a single click. Whether you're taking a break from work, studying, or simply browsing the web, this witty companion is here to add a dash of humor to your online routine.
